 class="speaker-podium wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="1.75s"></div><div class="col-xs-3 col-sm-3 col-md-3 scene-speaker-container"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/scene/optimized/scene-speaker-background-light.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="" class="speaker-background-light wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.5s"><div class="speaker-light wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="1.5s"></div><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/scene/speakers/optimized/speaker-alon-cohen.png?version=394C95A7BE794656" alt="Alon Cohen, President & Co-Founder, Houzz" class="speaker-podium wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="2.25s"></div><div class="col-xs-3 col-sm-3 col-md-3 scene-speaker-container"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/scene/optimized/scene-speaker-background-light.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="" class="speaker-background-light wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="0.75s"><div class="speaker-light wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="1.75s"></div><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/scene/speakers/optimized/speaker-daniel-alegre.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="Daniel Alegre, President, Retail & Shopping, Google" class="speaker-podium wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="2.75s"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="stats-container"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><p>Shoptalk is the World's Largest Conference for Retail & Ecommerce</p></div></div></div></div><div class="mailing-list-container"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><form method="POST" action="https://shoptalk.com/mailing-list/save" accept-charset="UTF-8" class="form-common" name="form_save_new_mailing_list_request" id="form_save_new_mailing_list_request" role="form" autocomplete="off" data-role="mailing-list-form"><input name="_token" type="hidden" value="NMD5rtbkzUVTgSXub0080E68qUkJACEbiMzWOHx6"><div class="row form-body"><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-2 form-title"><p>Join Mailing List</p><input type="text" name="name" class="input-form-name" value="" /><input type="email" name="email" class="input-form-email" value="" /></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5ths"><div class="form-group"><input class="form-control input-sm" placeholder="First Name" required="required" maxlength="50" name="first_name" type="text"></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5ths"><div class="form-group"><input class="form-control input-sm" placeholder="Last Name" required="required" maxlength="50" name="last_name" type="text"></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5ths"><div class="form-group"><input class="form-control input-sm" placeholder="Job Title" required="required" maxlength="50" name="title" type="text"></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-5ths"><div class="form-group"><input class="form-control input-sm" placeholder="Company" required="required" maxlength="50" name="company" type="text"></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5ths"><div class="form-group"><input class="form-control input-sm" placeholder="Email Address" required="required" maxlength="100" name="ea" type="email"></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-1 column-button"><div class="form-group"><button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-block btn-red btn-flash hvr-grow" name="form_submit" data-action="submit">Join</button></div></div></div><div class="row form-message hide"><div class="col-xs-12">Thank you for joining our Mailing List!</div></div></form></div></div></div></div><div class="countdown-container unselectable"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 column-ticket"><a href="https://shoptalk.com/register"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/countdown/optimized/ticket-icon.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="Get Your Ticket" class="ticket-icon"></a><p><a href="https://shoptalk.com/register">Get Your Ticket Now!</a></p></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 column-countdown"><div class="main-countdown"><div class="row centered text-center" id="shoptalk_countdown"></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class="section section-overview" id="overview"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h2 class="section-title">Overview</h2><h3 class="section-subtitle">Shoptalk Is The World’s Largest Conference <br class="hidden-sm hidden-xs">For Retail &amp; Ecommerce Innovation</h3><div class="section-content"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6"><p>Shoptalk covers the rapid evolution of how consumers discover, shop and buy—from new technologies and business models to the latest trends in consumer behaviors, preferences and expectations.</p><p>Established retailers and brands, startups, tech companies, investors, media, analysts and others come together at Shoptalk to learn, collaborate and evolve. Everyone benefits from rich interactions over four days packed with incredible content, wide-ranging exhibitors and productive networking.</p></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6"><p>Shoptalk 2018 will have more than 7,500 attendees, up almost 40% from 5,500 in 2017. As Shoptalk gets bigger, it only gets better by (1) maintaining audience seniority, (2) increasing facilitated and curated interactions, and (3) freshening content and speakers.</p><p><em>For 2018, we’re bringing our U.S. and European events together into one expansive event in Las Vegas to create the industry’s first global dialogue and community.</em></p></div></div><div class="charts"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/charts/optimized/charts.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="Overview Charts" class="horizontal"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/charts/optimized/charts-vertical.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="Overview Charts" class="vertical"></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="overview-quotes-container"><div class="overview-quotes-container-inner"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5 column-words"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/words/optimized/intro.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" class="wow fadeOutLeft" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="4s" alt="The 10 most common words program participants used to describe the program in a post-event survey:"><div class="words wow fadeIn" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="5s"><div class="words-inner"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/words/optimized/words.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt=""><div class="word word-valuable"></div><div class="word word-efficient"></div><div class="word word-helpful"></div><div class="word word-useful"></div><div class="word word-beneficial"></div><div class="word word-awesome"></div><div class="word word-informative"></div><div class="word word-excellent"></div><div class="word word-convenient"></div><div class="word word-worthwhile"></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-1"></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 column-quotes"><div class="slider-container"><div class="quotes-slider" id="quotes_slider"><ul><li class="slide"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/quotes/optimized/total-retail-logo.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="Total Retail">“Shoptalk, the retail and e-commerce mega conference that launched in 2016...has become a major player in the space.”</li><li class="slide"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/quotes/optimized/wwd-logo.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="WWD">“The inaugural Shoptalk conference… highlighted the discourse taking place from within, ranging from the broader macro trends impacting retail to diving into the weeds of high technology.”</li><li class="slide"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/quotes/optimized/the-robin-report-logo.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="The Robin Report">“Shoptalk 2016 gave me immense confidence that the talent is out there. Anil Aggarwal is a genius because he provided a forum for the convergence of these eclectic voices that will provide a playbook for the future of retail.”</li><li class="slide slide-the-huffington-post"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/quotes/optimized/the-huffington-post-logo.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="The Huffington Post">“If the retail world can agree on one thing, it is that the line up at Shoptalk 2016 is impressive… The retail industry has been waiting for an event like this.”</li><li class="slide"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/quotes/optimized/the-seattle-times-logo.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="The Seattle Times">“If one thing is clear at this gathering of the retail industry’s top brass, it is that pretty much everyone in the sector is figuring out how to beat, collaborate with or be the next Amazon.com.”</li><li class="slide"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/quotes/optimized/inc-logo.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="Inc.">“As someone who has attended or spoken at hundreds of conferences globally spanning more than two decades, I was blown away. Had you been there, you wouldn’t have believed that Shoptalk was in its inaugural year.”</li><li class="slide"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/quotes/optimized/wgsn-logo.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="WGSN">“Only in its first year, the conference is generating loads of buzz, with tickets selling out, even after organisers added an additional 1,000 slots.”</li><li class="slide"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/quotes/optimized/glossy-logo.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="Glossy">“At Shoptalk, practical tech is grabbing more dollars than sexy tech.”</li></ul></div><div class="border"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="overview-ticket-link"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 relative"><a href="https://shoptalk.com/register" class="link"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/overview/optimized/ticket-icon.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="Get Your Ticket" class="ticket-icon"><span>Get Your Ticket and Join the New Narrative and Community</span></a></div></div></div></div><section class="section section-retailers" id="retailers"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 column-message"><div class="jacket-container unselectable"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/retailers/optimized/jacket.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" alt="No Budget Required" class="img-jacket"><div class="jacket-message"></div><a href="#" class="jacket-link"></a></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 column-description"><h2 class="section-title">Retailers &amp; Brands</h2><h3 class="section-subtitle">You're Never Too Old To Learn!</h3><div class="section-content"><p>With disruptive changes throughout retail and ecommerce, now is the time to innovate, collaborate and partner in entirely new ways.</p><p>Thousands of individuals from hundreds of retailers and brands around the world attend Shoptalk to meet with their peers as well as with startups, tech companies, investors and others. Shoptalk’s environment is open, friendly and conducive to: (1) learning about the latest technologies, trends and business models and (2) interacting with the ecosystem to embrace innovation.</p><p>Established retailers and brands may qualify for complimentary tickets plus up to $750 in travel reimbursement ($1,000 if you stay onsite at the Venetian) as part of our <strong>Hosted Retailers & Brands Program</strong>. To qualify, you must be responsible for buying or evaluating retail or ecommerce technology or other solutions for their companies, and:</p></div></div></div><p><ol><li>Take up to eight (8) 15-minute onsite meetings with our exhibitors and sponsors, which we base on a combined opt-in and opt-out process so that they are useful to you (<em>a total of up to two hours</em>),</li><li>Visit at least two of four Discovery Zones in the Exhibit Hall where we will showcase the latest in Artificial Intelligence, Store of the Future, Emerging Technologies and Grocerytalk (<em>estimated one hour</em>).</li></ol></p><p><strong>Your eight (8) 15-minute meetings (total of up to only two hours) will be held during two to four of the following slots:</strong> 3/18 (Sunday) at 4:00-5:00 PM; 3/19 (Monday) at 8:00-9:00 AM; 3/19 at 12:40-1:40 PM; 3/20 (Tuesday) at 8:00-9:00 AM; 3/20 at 12:40-1:40 PM; and 3/21 (Wednesday) at 8:00-9:00 AM. Your final schedule will be sent to you prior to the event. <strong>You will not need to miss any agenda sessions for these meetings.</strong></p><p>Retailers and brands also qualify for special individual and group ticket rates. Subject to approval and available <a href="https://shoptalk.com/register" class="bright color-white underlined caps">here</a>.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="section section-startups" id="startups"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 column-description"><h2 class="section-title">B2C &amp; Tech Startups</h2><h3 class="section-subtitle">Step Up To A New Conversation & Community!</h3><div class="section-content"><p>More than 1,000 B2C and tech startups redefining retail and ecommerce attend Shoptalk each year from major global hubs. Shoptalk provides startups with an unparalleled opportunity to form important fundraising, product, distribution and other partnerships with retailers, brands, tech companies, investors, media, analysts and more.</p><p>Startups less than two years old that have raised less than $2 million at the time of Shoptalk, can <a href="https://shoptalk.com/register/startup" class="bright underlined caps">apply here</a> for a limited number of special <strong>startup rate tickets</strong> and <a href="https://shoptalk.com/sponsors/apply" class="bright underlined caps">here</a> for discounted <strong>startup exhibiting</strong> opportunities (including participation in the Hosted Retailers & Brands Program).</p><p>We also hold an onsite <strong>Startup Pitch contest</strong> with significant cash prizes. Only 15 spots are available so <a href="https://shoptalk.com/startup-pitch/apply" class="bright underlined caps">apply now</a>.</p><p class="shifted">Startups may also qualify for <a href="https://shoptalk.com/networking-program" class="bright underlined caps">Funding Founders</a>, a networking program that matches investors and startups at the right stage and from the right sector. To apply for Funding Founders, you must be a registered attendee and apply <a href="https://shoptalk.com/networking-program/funding-founders" class="bright underlined caps">here</a>. Note that all meetings require investors to opt-in so they can’t be guaranteed.</p></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 column-badges"><div class="badges-padding"><div class="badges-container unselectable"><a href="https://shoptalk.com/startup-pitch/apply" title="Startup Pitch"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/startups/optimized/badge-startup-pitch.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" class="badge-startup-pitch" alt="Startup Pitch" /></a><a href="https://shoptalk.com/networking-program/funding-founders" title="Funding Founders"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/startups/optimized/badge-funding-founders.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" class="badge-funding-founders" alt="Funding Founders" /></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section section-investors" id="investors"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><div class="line-container line-top"></div><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-5 column-emblem"><div class="emblem-inner unselectable"><a href="https://shoptalk.com/register"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/investors/optimized/emblem.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" class="img-emblem" alt="Join The Class of 2018"></a><div class="shine"></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-7 column-description"><h2 class="section-title">Investors</h2><div class="section-content"><p>More than 150 VC and PE firms attend Shoptalk each year from major global hubs. There's no better place for investors to find the latest innovations, meet the greatest disrupters and hear perspectives from established leaders to evaluate opportunities in the context of the market.</p><p>Investors also qualify for <a href="https://shoptalk.com/networking-program" class="bright color-red underlined caps">Funding Founders</a>, a networking program where we match investors and startups at the right stage and from the right sector. In 2018, we will facilitate more than 1,000 introductions and onsite meetings as part of Funding Founders. <a href="https://shoptalk.com/networking-program/funding-founders" class="bright color-red underlined caps">Apply&nbsp;here</a>.</p></div></div></div><div class="line-container line-bottom"></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section section-exhibit" id="exhibit"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-7 column-description"><h2 class="section-title">Exhibit &amp; Sponsor</h2><h3 class="section-subtitle">Don't Miss The Bus! Reach The Global <br class="hidden-sm hidden-xs">Retail & Ecommerce Ecosystem</h3><div class="section-content"><p>More than 400 companies exhibit at and sponsor Shoptalk. Shoptalk 2018 will be world’s biggest retail and ecommerce conference, offering technology companies and solution providers a uniquely large and exceptionally senior as well as international audience.</p><div class="button-container"><a href="https://shoptalk.com/sponsors/apply" class="btn btn-red btn-flash hvr-grow">Apply to Exhibit &amp; Sponsor</a><a href="https://shoptalk.com/sponsors" class="btn btn-red btn-flash hvr-grow btn-agenda">Current Sponsors</a></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-5 column-message"><div class="message-inner"><div class="sign"></div><div class="sign-text">SHOPTALK Presents an Unparalleled Opportunity To:</div><div class="message"><p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="1s"><i class="icon fa fa-star"></i>Build Brand Awareness</p><p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="1.25s"><i class="icon fa fa-star"></i>Engage With Decision Makers</p><p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s" data-wow-delay="1.5s"><i class="icon fa fa-star"></i>Launch New Products To The Industry and Media</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section section-speak" id="speak"><div class="container-fluid"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 p-l-0 p-r-0"><div class="bordered-container"><div class="bordered-container-inner"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 column-badge"><img src="https://shoptalk.com/assets/images/home/speak/optimized/badge.png?version=735C68FB949D8447" class="img-badge unselectable" alt="2018 Las Vegas"></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9 column-description"><h2 class="section-title">Speakers</h2><h3 class="section-subtitle">Our Faculty Is Transforming<br class="hidden-sm hidden-xs">Retail & Ecommerce!</h3><div class="section-content"><p>Shoptalk is primetime and Shoptalk’s 300+ speakers are industry leaders and innovators from a broad cross-section of countries and companies. Ranging from established retailers and brands to innovative new startups and prolific investors, over half of Shoptalk speakers are CEOs or founders and almost a quarter are from outside the U.S. We are no longer accepting speaker applications.</p><div class="button-container"><a href="https://shoptalk.com/speakers" class="btn btn-red btn-flash hvr-grow btn-agenda">Confirmed Speakers</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section section-agenda" id="agenda"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h2 class="section-title">Agenda</h2><h3 class="section-subtitle">Go Back To School At Shoptalk!</h3><div class="section-content"><p class="text-center">With over 100 groundbreaking sessions across more than a dozen tracks, Shoptalk leads the global retail and ecommerce industry narrative. It covers the latest technologies, trends and business models from across the globe as well as the rapid transformation of how consumers discover, shop and buy physical products, ranging from grocery to luxury and everything in between. The Shoptalk agenda includes important perspectives from an unparalleled group of U.S. and international leaders and innovators.</p><div class="button-container"><a href="https://shoptalk.com/schedule" class="btn btn-red btn-flash hvr-grow">Schedule</a><a href="https://shoptalk.com/agenda" class="btn btn-red btn-flash hvr-grow btn-agenda"><span class="icon"></span>Download Agenda</a></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class="section-media-pre"></div><section class="section section-media" id="media"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><h2 class="section-title">Media</h2><div class="section-content"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-5 column-description"><h4 class="section-column-subtitle">Cover Shoptalk Onsite</h4><p>More than 200 editorial staff from retail, ecommerce, tech, mainstream and other industry media as well as Wall Street analysts attend Shoptalk from the U.S., Europe, Asia and other regions. They cover more than 175 onsite announcements along with ​commentary from 300+ speakers and one​-​to​-​one interviews.</p><p>Approved editorial media are eligib